data.description: GREAT LOCATION & A HUGE FENCED-IN YARD!!!  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on .664 acre lot close to schools, shopping & dining. Main floor features 2 bedrooms, full bath, dine-in kitchen with oak cabinets, large great room with vaulted ceiling & utility/laundry room. Upstairs is the large master suite with full bath & walk-in closet. 2+ car heated garage (32x26) has full walk-up attic for  tons of extra storage & a there's also a garden shed (or a chicken coop if that's what you prefer)!
